<p><ent>Brevet</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Brevet
<hw>Bre*vet"</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>Taking or
conferring rank by brevet; <as>as, a <ex>brevet</ex> colonel; a
<ex>brevet</ex> commission</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brevetcy</ent>⟦br⟧
